bodyEn:
To: etoll.customers@icicibank.com

Subject: FASTag Dispute — Vehicle {VEHICLE_NO} — Txn {TXN_ID}

ICICI Bank FASTag team,

I am raising a dispute for a FASTag transaction on my ICICI FASTag (Vehicle: {VEHICLE_NO}, Tag ID: {TAG_ID}).

Txn ID: {TXN_ID}
Date & time: {TXN_DATETIME}
Toll plaza: {PLAZA_NAME}
Lane: {LANE_ID}
Amount: Rs. {AMOUNT}
Issue type: {ISSUE_TYPE}

Resolution requested: chargeback of Rs. {AMOUNT} to my FASTag wallet within 7 days. If no resolution, I will escalate to IHMCL (falsededuction@ihmcl.com) and the 1033 helpline.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

